# 止蝕
(pos:動詞)
<explanation>
yue:喺投資或者賭博輸錢嘅時候，及時收手唔再繼續，避免損失擴大（量詞：次）
eng:to cut losses; to stop loss
<eg>
yue:見到隻股票跌咗兩成，我即刻止蝕賣晒佢。 (gin3 dou2 zek3 gu2 piu3 dit3 zo2 loeng5 sing4, ngo5 zik1 hak1 zi2 sit6 maai6 saai3 keoi5.)
eng:When I saw the stock had dropped 20%, I immediately cut my losses and sold it all. [end of text]


